{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a specific criminal offence to lie about being bitten by a dog",
        "additional_details": "We are concerned that people are making false allegations as a way of attack. False accusations can cause a lot of stress on those involved. We think people who lie about being bitten by a dog should be held accountable with a hefty fine or imprisonment.",
        "background": "When people falsely accuse dogs of biting them dogs could be wrongly seized or even killed. This puts strain on dog owners, police and tax payers.",
